title: Vote: First and 10 Play of the Week for week 8
text:
Grandview Heights' Andre Readey finds James Lachey who fights his way in for a touchdown By 10TV Web Staff Monday October 19, 2015 12:03 AM UPDATED: Monday October 19, 2015 12:06 AM 
Vote for this week’s First and 10 Play of the Week. Your nominees are: Westerville Central's Daniel Rucker tips the ball to himself and returns the interception for a touchdown. Westerville Central's Benny Snell runs 82 yards for a touchdown Grandview Heights' Andre Readey finds James Lachey who fights his way in for a touchdown 
The winner will be announced during the sports segment of 10TV News at 6 on Tuesday ©2015 by 10TV.com. All rights reserved. This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed. Currently in Columbus
